text: Władysław Kuncewicz (born 23 October 1888, date of death unknown) was a Polish swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre freestyle event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Polish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Poland Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kazan Category:People from Kazan Governorate Category:Imperial Russian people of Polish descent Category:Polish people of the Polish–Soviet War
title: Władysław Kuncewicz
